Text: I am going to be seeding this every moment my computer is online, so dont let the 0 seeds discourage you. However, once you have finished downloading it, please seed at least a day, this collection is to large to let go to waste.
Just wanted to say thanks for the awesome collection, this gotta be one of the best collections available.

Strange that someone would upload 7.8GB of MP3 files. What a waste of space. I appreciate the fact that someone put the effort into finding these tracks and putting up here but it would have been so much easier to download and seed if they were all in their native .mod format.
When im finished downloading this, i will seed it forever when my computer is on :) Such awesomeness
